snippet.title: AMBER HEARD CALLED OUT BY KEVIN HART FOR LYING! | Depp Vs Heard Trial | CELEBRITY RESPONSE!
snippet.description:
In the midst of the defamation lawsuit trial between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, Amber continues to be exposed for lying. The latest being her false statement by her lawyer about a specific makeup palette she had used to cover alleged bruises from Johnny Depp (Heard's claim). The makeup company, "Milani Cosmetics", recently showed the date the palette came out (in 2017), which happens to be AFTER Amber's allegations and restraining order stint from Depp in which she accused him of domestic v. Kevin Hart has joined the humbling Heard bandwagon and calls her out in this EXCLUSIVE video!

#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #DeppVsHeardTrial
